            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Pulse 1.1.0

- Added a pinnable floating panel and compact minimal mode.
- Added CPU and memory process rankings with app icons, pixel share charts, and detail popovers.
- Refined full-panel status cards with System Runtime and stronger status feedback.
- Added Sparkle update checks and in-panel update installation.
- Added Appearance and Contact settings, and improved menu bar and floating panel layout.
]]></description>
